main_text: Asset tracking is essential across various industries, including logistics, manufacturing, healthcare, and security. These sectors require real-time visibility to track asset movement or misplacement, enhance supply chain efficiency, and prevent theft.​

The Renesas Asset Tracking and Locationing at Scale (ATLAS) offers a best-in-class tracking system, capable of tracking 500+ tags/locator/second or thousands (1000s) of tags/locator with precision down to 10cm, even in challenging RF environments. Specific implementations, such as the Telemos Locator developed in partnership with IOSEA, combined withsmart asset tracking labelsandBluetooth®Low Energy tags, allow for easy adaptation and fast time to market.
benefits: Real-time location and high-capacity tag tracking (1000s of tags, down to 10cm accuracy)​.
Compatible with the customer's existing Real-Time Locating System (RTLS) backend or IOSEA's best-in-class RTLS backend/microservice for scalable, efficient, and accurate real-time location tracking​.
Simultaneously support for Angle of Arrival (AoA), Angle of Departure (AoD), ATLAS, ATLASlite, Eddystone™, and iBeacon™ tags.

applications: Real-time location tracking of assets, inventory, pets, staff, and livestock
Theme parks, stadiums, and cruise ships
